              "RetainInterval": {
                "type": "integer",
                "description": "<p> <b>[Default policies only]</b> Specifies how long the policy should retain snapshots or AMIs before deleting them. The retention period can range from 2 to 14 days, but it must be greater than the creation frequency to ensure that the policy retains at least 1 snapshot or AMI at any given time. If you do not specify a value, the default is 7.</p> <p>Default: 7</p>",
